==Enemy Stats Structure==

Each enemy entry is '''74 bytes ($4a)''' starting at ROM offset '''$014275''' (unheadered).

===Enemy Stats Table Format===

{| class="wikitable"
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00-$01 || word || Max HP (little-endian)
