| $02 || byte || Level
|-
| $03 || byte || Attack Power
|-
| $04 || byte || Defense
|-
| $05 || byte || Speed
|-
| $06 || byte || Magic Power
|-
| $07 || byte || Accuracy
|-
| $08 || byte || Evasion
|-
| $09 || byte || Magic Defense
|-
