|-
| $0b || byte || EXP reward (mid byte)
|-
| $0c || byte || EXP reward (high byte)
|-
| $0d || byte || Gold reward (low byte)
|-
| $0e || byte || Gold reward (mid byte)
|-
| $0f || byte || Gold reward (high byte)
|-
| $10 || byte || Elemental weaknesses bitflags
|-
| $11 || byte || Elemental resistances bitflags
|-
| $12 || byte || Status immunities bitflags
|-
| $13 || byte || Status vulnerabilities bitflags
|-
| $14-$1f || 12 bytes || Attack pattern data (attack IDs and probabilities)
|-
| $20-$2f || 16 bytes || Battle AI script pointers/data
|-
| $30-$39 || 10 bytes || Sprite/graphics data pointers
|-
